The paper discusses the application of information theory in algebraic code design, specifically in analyzing the unit group of orders of certain division algebras. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AL (Algorithms), cs.NT (Number Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
